it most. For the last 3 years, Dr. Jesse Chai and his team at Bradford Family Dentistry have donated their time and resources to host this event in downtown Bradford West Gwillimbury. This year Dr. Chai and his team were able to donate $28,800 worth of FREE DENTAL CARE to more than 100 people.\r\n\r\nFor more information, please visit his <a href="http://youtu.be/lB0OlFQwr_k">YouTube Video</a> about last years event.\r\n\r\nTo connect with us, please visit our website at: <a href="http://www.bradfordfamilydentist.ca">http://www.bradfordfamilydentist.ca </a>\r\n<h3>__________________________________</h3>\r\n<h3>Silver Sponsor</h3>\r\n<img class="size-full wp-image-373 alignleft" alt="Shanahan Ford Logo" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Shanahan-Ford-Logo.png" width="300" height="180" />\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Over a century ago in 1880, David Shanahan, a young blacksmith, started building horse-drawn buggies and sleighs in Penetanguishene, Ontario. This was the beginning of the Shanahan Carriage Co. Ltd. Today, Shanahan Ford stands out as a community leader as they support the community through events like Bradford Ribfest 2013 and now Bradfordlicious 2014</span>.\r\n\r\nShanahan knows that you have high expectations, and as a car dealer they enjoy the challenge of meeting and exceeding those standards each and every time. Allow them to demonstrate their commitment to excellence! Their experienced sales staff is eager to share its knowledge and enthusiasm with you.\r\n\r\nTo connect with us, please visit our website at: <a href="http://shanahan.dealerconnection.com">http://shanahan.dealerconnection.com</a>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<img class="size-full wp-image-367 alignleft" alt="Midas Logo" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Midas-Logo.png" width="300" height="180" />\r\n\r\nBradford Midas is pleased to be a Silver Sponsor of Bradfordlicious 2014. Whether you need an oil change or tires, factory recommended maintenance, or brake repair, your local Midas has you covered.\r\n\r\nBradford Midas is family owned and operated and is dedicated to providing high quality auto repair service at a fair price. And their work is backed by our famous Midas Guarantee.\r\n\r\nTo connect with us, please vista our website at: <a href="http://www.midas.com/bradford/store.aspx?shopnum=9007&amp;dmanum=77002">http://www.midas.com</a>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h3>__________________________________</h3>\r\n<h3>Bronze Sponsor</h3>\r\n<img class="size-full wp-image-377 alignleft" alt="photo copy" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/photo-copy.png" width="300" height="180" />MarlinTravel in Bradford are very pleased to sponsor Bradfordlicious 2014. <span style="line-height: 1.5em;">\r\n</span>\r\n\r\nMarlin Travel’s mission is to supply a rich platform of products that will enable our customers to enjoy a gratifying vacation purchase experience and a long term viable and trusting relationship with each of our travel advisors.\r\n\r\nMarlin Travel is a Canadian company and a proud member of Transat A.T. Inc., one of the largest vertically intergrated tourism companies in the world and Canada''s holiday travel leader. For more information, visit them today in the Walmart Plaza on Holland Street.\r\n\r\nTo connect with us, please visit our website at: <a href="http://www.marlintravel.ca/travel-agencies/bradford/bradford-holland-st-42538">http://www.marlintravel.ca</a>\r\n<h3>__________________________________</h3>\r\n<h3>Media Sponsor</h3>\r\n<a href="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-Times-Logo.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-372 alignleft" alt="Bradford Times Logo" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-Times-Logo.png" width="300" height="180" /></a>The Bradford Times has been serving the <a title="Bradford West Gwillimbury" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bradford_West_Gwillimbury">Bradford West Gwillimbury</a>, south <a title="Innisfil, Ontario" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Innisfil,_Ontario">Innisfil</a> and <a title="Holland Marsh" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Holland_Marsh">Holland Marsh</a> areas for over 18 years – covering local Town Council, charity and cultural events, sports and business news. It is delivered free by carrier, throughout its distribution area.\r\n\r\nBradfordlicious 2014 is proudly sponsored by the Bradford Times. Their partnership helps make this inargural event a wonderful success.\r\n\r\nTo connect with us, please visit our website at: <a href="http://www.bradfordtimes.ca">http://www.bradfordtimes.ca</a>', 'Sponsors', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '224-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-20 03:07:14', '2014-01-20 03:07:14', '', 224, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=423', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
