(474, 1, '2014-01-22 08:00:15', '2014-01-22 08:00:15', '[details address="1812 County 27, Bradford West Gwillimbury, ON L0G 1T0" latitude="44.04009" longitude="-79.66371" phone="(905)-939-7777" website="www.1812grillhouse.com"\r\nhours="Mon &amp; Tues closed,  Wed 4pm - 10pm,  Thurs &amp; Fri 4pm - 1am,  Sat 12pm - 1am,  Sun 2pm - 8pm"]\r\n\r\nLet a team with over 25 years of combined experience in the hospitality industry provide you top-shelf service in what we love to do!\r\nA group of dynamic hospitality industry leaders came together in 2012 to create 1812 GrillHouse. The demand for innovative event solutions outside of the GTA as well as the desire for successful events in the social and private sectors became the focus of our company. As a client of 1812 GrillHouse, you will be immersed in the top talent this town has to offer that will create a memorable experience with unparalleled service. A completely seamless execution will provide you with a professional event filled with sophistication, flare and uniqueness.\r\n<h1>BRADFORDLICIOUS SPECIAL</h1>\r\n<h2>Appetizers (pick one)</h2>\r\n1812 Organic Greens with Roasted Pecan Balsamic dressing\r\n\r\nSouthern Chicken &amp; Shrimp Gumbo\r\n\r\nJalapeno Corn &amp; Cheddar Muffins with Apple Butter\r\n<h2>Entrees (pick one)</h2>\r\nSouthern Fried Chicken &amp; Waffles\r\n\r\nJambalaya Louisiana\r\n\r\nChicken Fried Steak\r\n<h2>Dessert</h2>\r\nPeanut Butter Mud Pie &amp; Ice Cream\r\n\r\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nDrinks, Taxes &amp; Gratuity are extra. Excludes Valentines Day and Family Day. Call ahead for reservations.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', '1812 Grillhouse', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '157-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-22 08:00:15', '2014-01-22 08:00:15', '', 157, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=474', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(477, 1, '2014-01-22 08:03:22', '2014-01-22 08:03:22', '[details address="136 Holland St E #1, Bradford, ON L3Z 2B7" latitude="44.11533" longitude="-79.56013"  phone="(905)551-1600 " hours="Sun, Mon, Wed 11am - 8pm, Thurs - Sat 11am - 9pm,  Tues - Closed"]\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Bangkok Saigon Noodle, offering a fusion of Thai and Vietnamese food. Owners Heuang Souvannalath and Kevin Theng have come up with a menu that provides a range of taste experiences - from crispy spring rolls, to Satays and Pad Thai noodle dishes, and from mild to hot. Specialties include "Drunken Noodles", cooked in white wine, and a Mango salad that is both refreshing, and has bite!</span>\r\n\r\nAll dishes are freshly made in Bangkok Saigon Noodle''s kitchens, with great attention to detail, and to the customer''s spicy preferences.\r\n<table width="127" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><colgroup> <col width="127" /></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="xl65" style="height: 19.95pt; width: 95pt;" width="127" height="26"><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;">(905) 775-1688</span></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Bangkok Saigon', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '386-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-22 08:03:22', '2014-01-22 08:03:22', '', 386, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=477', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
